# StoneRise ICP & Persona Targeting

Reference doc: `Marketing/StoneRise-ICP.md`

## Core ICP

| Attribute | Ideal | Acceptable |
|-----------|-------|------------|
| Geography | United Kingdom | UK-based |
| Industry | Construction main contractors, subcontractors | Any built environment contractor |
| Turnover | £10m – £50m | £5m – £100m |
| Employees | 50 – 200 | 11 – 500 |
| Monthly PO Volume | 200+ | 100+ |

## Four Buyer Personas

| Persona | Key Job Titles | Decision Authority |
|---------|---------------|-------------------|
| **Commercial Leader** | Commercial Director, QS Director, Head of Commercial | High |
| **Finance Leader** | Finance Director, FD, Financial Controller, CFO | High |
| **Procurement Leader** | Procurement Manager, Procurement Director, Head of Procurement, Buying Manager | Medium-High |
| **Operations Leader** | Managing Director, MD, Operations Director, CEO, Owner | Highest |

## Michael vs Stelios Targeting Split

| | Michael Loizias | Stelios Ioannou |
|---|---|---|
| **Primary Persona** | Commercial Leader | Finance Leader |
| **Secondary Persona** | Procurement Leader, Tech-forward MDs | Business-focused MDs |
| **Content Angle** | Product features, technical deep-dives, QS workflows, building in public | ROI, business case, margin protection, scaling efficiency |
| **Tone** | Enthusiastic builder, practitioner | Strategic advisor, financial rigour |

### Michael's LinkedIn Targeting

**Include:** Commercial Director, Commercial Manager, QS Director, Head of Commercial, Operations Director, Technical Director, Procurement Manager, Procurement Director, Head of Procurement, Buying Manager

**Exclude:** Finance Director, Financial Controller, CFO

### Stelios's LinkedIn Targeting

**Include:** Finance Director, FD, Financial Controller, CFO, Managing Director, MD, Owner, CEO, Founder

**Exclude:** Commercial Director, QS Director, Procurement Director (these go to Michael)

## Exclusions (Never Target)

- Recruiters / Staffing agencies
- Software vendors / SaaS companies
- Marketing agencies / Consultants
- Tier 1 contractors (Balfour Beatty, Skanska, etc.)
- Non-UK companies

## Post Tagging

Every LinkedIn post should include a target persona tag:

```
<!-- Target: Commercial Leader -->
<!-- Target: Finance Leader -->
<!-- Target: Procurement Leader -->
<!-- Target: Operations Leader -->
```

## Quick Reference

- **Procurement titles ARE now included** — Procurement Manager, Director, Head of Procurement are valid targets
- Michael owns Commercial + Procurement personas
- Stelios owns Finance + Operations (MD/FD) personas
- No scatter-gun approach — every post and connection should map to a specific persona
